INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES ('29', '1', '2010-05-25 10:20:44', '2010-05-25 10:20:44', '[singlepic id=33 w=199 h=300 float=right]\n<h3>Our Mission</h3>\nLife is full of the extraordinary – in events, sights, situations and people – it’s all around us. We believe that by highlighting and sharing the extraordinary with each other, life becomes a richer and more entertaining experience.\n<h3>What we offer</h3>\nOur vision is to create a unique entertainment destination – the site of choice for people who seek and share extraordinary content. We offer you the ability to browse our selection of extraordinary videos and pictures, upload your videos or send us any pictures of interest - where you can then share it with your friends.\n\n[singlepic id=34 w=300 h=200 float=left]\n\n<h3>Welcome to the extraordinary film competition</h3>\nAs part of the launch of “welcome to the extraordinary” we are partnering with Raindance, (who showcase independent film through their annual film festival) and Mathew Horne the leading actor who plays Gavin in the critically acclaimed “Gavin and Stacey” to create a competition with some great prizes including an - access all areas trip to the 2011 Cannes Film Festival. Find out more about the competition here. \n\n<h3>What kind of things are here?</h3>\nAnything that you, as a user considers to be extraordinary, whether this be an amazing act of human endurance or the height of the Burj Khalifa (the tallest building in the world). If you know of something extraordinary – share it with everyone! We offer you some of the world’s most amazing and interesting videos, pictures and other media with the ability for you rate and comment submissions.\n<h3>InterCasino</h3>\nWelcome to the extraordinary is powered by Intercasino and has been set up to create a unique entertainment destination that will appeal to the hearts and minds of our customers, enabling them to explore and celebrate the extraordinary – a place where they can share their extraordinary and exceptional content.', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '6-autosave', '', '', '2010-05-25 10:20:44', '2010-05-25 10:20:44', '', '6', 'http://webtrendz.co.uk/extraordinary/2010/03/6-autosave/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
