INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES ('127', '1', '2010-03-24 12:09:50', '2010-03-24 12:09:50', '<strong>Lead page copy: </strong>Calling all filmmakers!  InterCasino has teamed up with Raindance to launch an extraordinary short film competition.\r\n\r\nFind out <a title=\"The Brief\" href=\"http://webtrendz.co.uk/extraordinary/the-brief/\" target=\"_self\">more</a> about how your 40-second film could win you a screening at the Raindance Film Festival and a trip to Cannes 2011.<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"> </span>\r\n\r\n<span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"> </span>\r\n\r\n<strong>The Extraordinary</strong>\r\n\r\nThe extraordinary is a feeling, a destination, a state of mind. It’s an escape, a release.  InterCasino, the world’s first online casino, offers players an extraordinary gaming experience.\r\n\r\nWe want you to express what extraordinary means to you in your short film.  Looking for inspiration?  Take a look at the films below, or read more about the extraordinary <a title=\"The Extraordinary\" href=\"http://webtrendz.co.uk/extraordinary/the-extraordinary/\" target=\"_self\">here</a>.', 'homepage', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '12-revision-15', '', '', '2010-03-24 12:09:50', '2010-03-24 12:09:50', '', '12', 'http://webtrendz.co.uk/extraordinary/2010/03/12-revision-15/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES ('151', '1', '2010-04-26 08:56:10', '2010-04-26 08:56:10', '<strong>The Welcome to the Extraordinary film competition is giving you a chance to try your hand at writing, producing and directing a short film.</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>InterCasino and Raindance</strong> are looking for short films that celebrate the extraordinary.  Whether you’re an experienced filmmaker or if this is the first time you’ve picked up a video camera, this competition is open to everyone.\r\n\r\nEach film must be less than<strong> 40.0</strong> seconds in length, to include an end frame supplied by InterCasino.\r\n\r\n<strong>What’s extraordinary?</strong>\r\n\r\nThe extraordinary is a feeling, a destination, a state of mind. It’s an escape, a release. A journey that takes what is usual, familiar or unremarkable and turbo-charges, elevates and magnifies it into a surreal, joyous, surprising, mind-bending, intensified version of itself.\r\n\r\nSo open yourself to be taken on an exhilarating adventure. It takes a small leap of faith, a gamble, an open mind.\r\n\r\nTake a look. Use your senses. Dip into a new world. Welcome to the extraordinary.\r\n\r\n<a title=\"Submit your video\" href=\"../upload/\" target=\"_self\">Submit  your film</a>\r\n\r\n<em>Additional content required for page:</em>\r\n\r\n-     <em>Film-type imagery?</em>', 'Meet us', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '6-revision-21', '', '', '2010-04-26 08:56:10', '2010-04-26 08:56:10', '', '6', 'http://webtrendz.co.uk/extraordinary/2010/04/6-revision-21/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
