INSERT INTO `wp_posts` VALUES ('150', '1', '2010-03-24 12:36:40', '2010-03-24 12:36:40', '<strong>The Welcome to the Extraordinary film competition is giving you a chance to try your hand at writing, producing and directing a short film.</strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>InterCasino and Raindance</strong> are looking for short films that celebrate the extraordinary.  Whether you’re an experienced filmmaker or if this is the first time you’ve picked up a video camera, this competition is open to everyone.\r\n\r\nEach film must be less than<strong> 40.0</strong> seconds in length, to include an end frame supplied by InterCasino.\r\n\r\n<strong>What’s extraordinary?</strong>\r\n\r\nThe extraordinary is a feeling, a destination, a state of mind. It’s an escape, a release. A journey that takes what is usual, familiar or unremarkable and turbo-charges, elevates and magnifies it into a surreal, joyous, surprising, mind-bending, intensified version of itself.\r\n\r\nSo open yourself to be taken on an exhilarating adventure. It takes a small leap of faith, a gamble, an open mind.\r\n\r\nTake a look. Use your senses. Dip into a new world. Welcome to the extraordinary.\r\n\r\n<a title=\"Submit your video\" href=\"../upload/\" target=\"_self\">Submit  your film</a>\r\n\r\n<em>Additional content required for page:</em>\r\n\r\n-     <em>Film-type imagery?</em>', 'The Brief', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '6-revision-20', '', '', '2010-03-24 12:36:40', '2010-03-24 12:36:40', '', '6', 'http://webtrendz.co.uk/extraordinary/2010/03/6-revision-20/', '0', 'revision', '', '0');
